Package: prism-monitor
Version: __VERSION__
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, coreutils, grep, sed, nodejs (>= 18), mysql-server (>= 8.0), mysql-client | default-mysql-client, python3 (>= 3.10), python3-psutil, python3-mysql.connector
Maintainer: PRISM Team
Description: PRISM full stack monitoring platform
 PRISM installs the Python collector, Node.js API, built React dashboard, systemd services,
 and database initialization helper for Ubuntu deployments.